1. *Kakvom* metodom ćemo izvršiti analizu podataka? (What method will we use to analyze the data?)
2. Svakom *kakvom* prilikom volim da posetim rođake u tom gradu. (I like to visit my relatives in that city on any occasion.)
3. Ne znam *kakvom* vrstom hrane bih se najviše obradovao. (I don't know what kind of food I would be most happy with.)
4. *Kakvom* srećom, uspeli smo da završimo projekat na vreme. (Fortunately, we managed to finish the project on time.)
5. *Kakvom* odlukom želiš da rešiš ovaj problem? (What decision do you want to make to solve this problem?)
6. Izuzetno mi je važno da saznam *kakvom* situacijom se suočavaju klijenti. (It is extremely important for me to find out what kind of situation clients are facing.)

Note: In Serbian, "kakvom" is a form of the pronoun "kakav" which means "what kind of".